name: R4B-ImagingStudy-R5-ImagingStudy
title: Concept map to convert a FHIR R4B ImagingStudy into FHIR R5

element.display: A set of images produced in single study (one or more series of references images)

target.display: A set of images produced in single study (one or more series of references images)
target.comment: R4B `ImagingStudy` maps as Equivalent to R5 `ImagingStudy`
R4B `ImagingStudy.basedOn` maps as Equivalent to R5 `ImagingStudy.basedOn`
R4B `ImagingStudy.contained` maps as Equivalent to R5 `ImagingStudy.contained`
R4B `ImagingStudy.description` maps as Equivalent to R5 `ImagingStudy.description`

element.display: Encounter with which this imaging study is associated

target.display: Encounter with which this imaging study is associated
target.comment: R4B `ImagingStudy.encounter` maps as Equivalent to R5 `ImagingStudy.encounter`
R4B `ImagingStudy.endpoint` maps as Equivalent to R5 `ImagingStudy.endpoint`
R4B `ImagingStudy.extension` maps as RelatedTo to R5 `ImagingStudy.extension` - extension has change due to type change: R4B `extension` `Extension` maps as RelatedTo for R5 `extension`
R4B `ImagingStudy.id` maps as Equivalent to R5 `ImagingStudy.id`
R4B `ImagingStudy.identifier` maps as Equivalent to R5 `ImagingStudy.identifier`

element.display: A set of rules under which this content was created

target.display: A set of rules under which this content was created
target.comment: R4B `ImagingStudy.implicitRules` maps as Equivalent to R5 `ImagingStudy.implicitRules`
R4B `ImagingStudy.language` maps as RelatedTo to R5 `ImagingStudy.language` - language made the binding required (from Preferred) for http://hl7.org/fhir/ValueSet/all-languages|5.0.0
R4B `ImagingStudy.location` maps as Equivalent to R5 `ImagingStudy.location`
R4B `ImagingStudy.meta` maps as Equivalent to R5 `ImagingStudy.meta`

element.display: All series modality if actual acquisition modalities

target.display: All of the distinct values for series' modalities
target.comment: R4B `ImagingStudy.modality` maps as SourceIsBroaderThanTarget to R5 `ImagingStudy.modality` - modality has change due to type change: R4B modality Coding has no equivalent or mapped type in R5 modality

R4B `ImagingStudy.modifierExtension` maps as RelatedTo to R5 `ImagingStudy.modifierExtension` - modifierExtension has change due to type change: R4B `modifierExtension` `Extension` maps as RelatedTo for R5 `modifierExtension`
R4B `ImagingStudy.note` maps as SourceIsNarrowerThanTarget to R5 `ImagingStudy.note` - note has change due to type change: R4B `note` `Annotation` maps as SourceIsNarrowerThanTarget for R5 `note`
R4B `ImagingStudy.numberOfInstances` maps as Equivalent to R5 `ImagingStudy.numberOfInstances`
R4B `ImagingStudy.numberOfSeries` maps as Equivalent to R5 `ImagingStudy.numberOfSeries`
R4B `ImagingStudy.referrer` maps as Equivalent to R5 `ImagingStudy.referrer`

element.display: Each study has one or more series of instances

target.display: Each study has one or more series of instances
target.comment: R4B `ImagingStudy.series` maps as Equivalent to R5 `ImagingStudy.series`

R4B `ImagingStudy.series.bodySite` maps as SourceIsBroaderThanTarget to R5 `ImagingStudy.series.bodySite` - bodySite has change due to type change: R4B bodySite Coding has no equivalent or mapped type in R5 bodySite
